		<item>
		<title>Uber offers free ride for DNCC Spring Media Walkthrough</title>
		<link>http://theppl.us/blog/671</link>
		<comments>http://theppl.us/blog/671#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Thu, 24 May 2012 05:33:31 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator>Corey Conner</dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[Blog]]></category>

		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://theppl.us/?p=671</guid>
		<description><![CDATA[There&#8217;s no need to stand on the street and hail a cab for the DNCC Spring Media Walkthrough. The DNCC and Uber, an app-driven private car service, have partnered up to offer transportation including a free first ride, up to $40. Uber, available in the iPhone and Android app stores handles calling a driver, and [...]]]></description>
			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>There&#8217;s no need to stand on the street and hail a cab for the DNCC Spring Media Walkthrough. The DNCC and <a href="http://uber.com">Uber</a>, an app-driven private car service, have partnered up to offer transportation including a free first ride, up to $40.</p>
<p><a href="http://uber.com"> Uber</a>, available in the iPhone and Android app stores handles calling a driver, and  keeps the user&#8217;s credit card on file to take care of the tip.</p>
<p>Here&#8217;s the information on how to sign up:</p>
<blockquote><p><strong>To take your first ride, follow the steps below:</strong></p>
<ol start="1">
<li>~5-10 minutes before you are ready to travel, open the app and move the pin to your location.  You can also text your address to 827-222 (e.g. 501 South College Street, Charlotte, NC 28202) or input it directly at <span style="text-decoration: underline;"><a href="http://m.uber.com/" target="_blank">m.uber.com</a></span>.</li>
<li>Submit your request and watch as your private driver is dispatched.  You will receive an estimate of when your driver will arrive and a text message when your driver is arriving.</li>
</ol>
<p>Want more information on Uber in at the Spring Media Walkthrough?  Head to:  <span style="text-decoration: underline;"><a href="http://www.uber.com/dncc" target="_blank">http://www.uber.com/dncc</a></span></p>
<p>Questions?  Email <a href="mailto:supportdncc@uber.com" target="_blank">supportdncc@uber.com</a></p></blockquote>
